info: Rating, 1 star,  · April 2024,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment:
As a person he is great but as a host he is not at all. He has issues with his building management and he is telling me to adjust with it.
There is no pool or gym for free. You must pay for that. And it’s a lot of money.
There is no dedicated work place. The wifi is a mess and he will ask you to buy your own internet. The building management team is not friendly at all and never smiles.
Do not give him your phone number because he keeps calling at the middle of the night if you send a text to Airbnb apps. He doesn’t want to communicate over the apps but on the phone or wtsap . Don’t fall for it. Airbnb should rethink about his super-host status.
I DO NOT RECOMMEND MAATI PROPERTIES TO MY WORST ENEMIES.
